Background

Possibly the first recorded visit, by a Sydney Uni party (Helen Whitfield, Karl Robertson, Dave Beattie, Gerry O’Byrne): https://www.subw.org.au/archives/press-on-regardless/newnes-glen-davis-return/. They swim under an arch into what sounds like the "Doomsday pool".
